data.description:
Gorgeous 4-bedroom home with a study and bonus/media room located in the esteemed Edmond North school district. This residence boasts all four bedrooms on the main level and an optional fifth bedroom upstairs with a full bath. The kitchen is well-appointed with a breakfast bar, dining area, granite counters, stainless steel gas stove, and a spacious walk-in pantry. The primary bedroom is generously sized, featuring an en-suite bath with a jetted tub, double vanities, a walk-in shower, and a closet that conveniently connects to the laundry room. Each secondary bedroom includes a walk-in closet, providing ample space for guests, a growing household, or multi-generational living.

The living room is expansive and features a corner fireplace and surround sound. The upstairs is wired for surround sound and a projector. Conveniently located within walking distance to the neighborhood park/pool and pond, and just minutes away from shopping, grocery stores, restaurants, schools, Edmond's lacrosse field and soccer fields, churches, and Mitch Park, which offers basketball courts, multiple playgrounds, picnic areas, a sound stage, YMCA, skate park, tennis courts, frisbee golf, walking trails, and more.

The roof was replaced five years ago, and both AC units and furnaces were replaced in 2020. With all these features and amenities, this home has everything you could ask for. Don't hesitate—browse the photos and schedule your private viewing today!
